{"_path":"/maps/_database/postgres","_dir":"_database","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Postgres","description":"PostgreSQL 是一个强大的开源关系型数据库，通过丰富的插件生态可以覆盖多种数据场景。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"扩展生态"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"扩展生态"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"postgres-能替代哪些专用数据库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Postgres 能替代哪些专用数据库？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传统架构中不同用途使用不同数据库：搜索用 Elasticsearch、缓存用 Redis、队列用 Kafka。但 Postgres 通过插件生态可以覆盖所有这些场景：全文搜索、JSON 存储、地理信息、消息队列等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这种\"一专多能\"的选型思路可以显著降低技术栈复杂度，特别适合中小团队。当数据库的扩展性足够好时，单一工具往往比多工具组合更具维护优势。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#周刊摘录 见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/articles/weekly-385"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"科技周刊第385期"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"扩展生态","depth":2,"text":"扩展生态"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_database:postgres:index.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_database/postgres/index.md","_stem":"6.maps/_database/postgres/index","_extension":"md"}